---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Worship — Alexander Cherry"
  description="A village-god simulator built in Java — resource allocation, belief systems, and natural disasters."
>
  <div class="page">
    <nav class="page-nav">
      <a href="/" class="back-link">
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M19 12H5M12 5l-7 7 7 7"/>
        </svg>
        Alexander Cherry
      </a>
    </nav>

    <header class="project-header">
      <div class="project-meta">
        <span class="meta-tag">Game</span>
        <span class="meta-tag">Java</span>
        <span class="meta-tag">Simulation</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="project-title"><span class="accent">Worship</span></h1>
      <p class="project-lead">
        A top-down village-god simulator. Play as a deity managing a civilization — resource
        allocation, belief systems, natural disasters, and the limits of divine power.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="project-gallery">
      <img
        src="/worship/images/worship-demoA.png"
        alt="Worship game screenshot showing the village overview"
        class="gallery-img"
        loading="eager"
      />
      <img
        src="/worship/images/worship-demoB.png"
        alt="Worship game screenshot showing village activity"
        class="gallery-img"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </section>

    <section class="project-body">
      <div class="project-section">
        <h2 class="section-label">About</h2>
        <p class="body-text">
          Worship is a god-game. An initially small village faces resource scarcity, earthquakes,
          and plagues. As their deity, your job is to provide for them through godly powers — but
          those powers aren't infinite. They run on belief.
        </p>
        <p class="body-text">
          If the people believe, they'll do as you say and you can grant them miracles. If they
          lose faith, your powers slowly wither. The game is built around this tension: intervention
          costs belief, but doing nothing costs survival.
        </p>
        <p class="body-text">
          Built in Java using the Processing animation library, with about 50 classes covering
          custom behavior trees, world generation, resource systems, and event logic.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="project-section">
        <h2 class="section-label">Demo</h2>
        <video class="project-video" controls preload="metadata">
          <source src="/worship/images/worship-demo2.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
          Your browser does not support video playback.
        </video>
      </div>

      <div class="project-section">
        <h2 class="section-label">Stack</h2>
        <div class="stack-row">
          <span class="stack-tag">Java</span>
          <span class="stack-tag">Processing</span>
          <span class="stack-tag">Behavior Trees</span>
          <span class="stack-tag">World Generation</span>
          <span class="stack-tag">Simulation</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="page-footer">
      <a href="/" class="back-link">← Back to portfolio</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page {
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 2.5rem 6rem;
  }

  /* Nav */
  .page-nav {
    padding: 1.5rem 0 3rem;
  }

  .back-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink);
    opacity: 0.5;
    transition: opacity 200ms var(--ease-out), color 200ms var(--ease-out);
  }

  .back-link:hover {
    opacity: 1;
    color: var(--cherry);
  }

  /* Header */
  .project-header {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .project-meta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .meta-tag {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--cherry);
    padding: 4px 10px;
    background: rgba(192, 57, 43, 0.06);
    border-radius: 100px;
  }

  .project-title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(52px, 9vw, 88px);
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .accent {
    color: var(--cherry);
  }

  .project-lead {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--ink);
    opacity: 0.85;
    max-width: 560px;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* Gallery */
  .project-gallery {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1px;
    background: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.06);
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .gallery-img {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 4/3;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    background: var(--cream-warm);
  }

  /* Body */
  .project-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.08);
    padding-top: 3rem;
  }

  .section-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--cherry);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .body-text {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: var(--ink);
    opacity: 0.85;
    max-width: 620px;
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .body-text:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .project-video {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: #1a1a1a;
    display: block;
  }

  .stack-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .stack-tag {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.12);
    border-radius: 4px;
    color: var(--ink);
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  /* Footer */
  .page-footer {
    margin-top: 5rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.08);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .page {
      padding: 1.5rem 1.5rem 5rem;
    }

    .project-gallery {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
